OL,6,FPolice are looking for a 59-year-old
OL,7,Fman who has been convicted of making a
OL,8,Fstring of "disgusting" and "perverse"
OL,9,Fcalls to the emergency service.
OL,11,FMark Clayton, from , bombarded the
OL,12,Fpolice control room's 101 number with
OL,13,Finappropriate calls and comments
OL,14,Fduring two days in October last year.
OL,16,FHe made 19 calls in which he discussed
OL,17,Fhis sex life in a perverse way and
OL,18,Fmade false accusations, said.
OL,20,FAn investigation was launched after
OL,21,Fcall handlers voiced their concerns.
