OL,7,Fwith sending offensive, obscene,
OL,8,Findecent and menacing messages but
OL,9,Ffailed to appear at and was found
OL,10,Fguilty in his absence.
OL,12,FA warrant for his arrest has been
OL,13,Fissued.
OL,15,FCh Supt Cherie Buttle said:"Our call
OL,16,Fhandlers come to work to help people
OL,17,Fand serve their communities.
OL,19,F"They deserve to be treated with
OL,20,Frespect and not spoken to with such
OL,21,Fdisgusting comments and suggestions.
